127
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,600
Don't worry.

128
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,600
Don't worry.

129
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:32,920
I'm here for you.

130
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,800
I'm here for you.

131
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,360
No one will beat you.

132
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
No one will beat you.

133
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:38,040
No one will beat you.

134
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,640
No one will beat you.

